704657f-a.title: Brooklyn: Goodwin Place - Greene Avenue
704657f-a.text:
Goodwin Place, south side, between Greene Ave., and Grove Street. The building in the center, housed the Bauman Storage Ce.; now eccupied by H.C. Bohack & Ce., (1929). The upper atory was detroyed by fire in 1923.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
